GRAPH <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ns__CadenceRhythm> {
  <https://aswritten.ai/narrative#Digest_ns__CadenceRhythm> a narr:Digest ;
    narr:digestOf <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#CadenceRhythm> ;
    narr:childCount "7"^^xsd:integer ;
    narr:generatedFrom "a01ed5a7f29cbdc52073bd24de69efc613d70c05" ;
    narr:narration """This hub catalogs the document's rhythmic and rhetorical architecture. The primary engine is a [git-native triad](narr:Observation_GitNativeTriad) that anchors technical concepts in parallel -able suffixes, a pattern mirrored in [triadic lists](narr:StyleObs_10) designed for memorability. This structured cadence is frequently disrupted by [rhetorical questions](narr:StyleObs_RhetoricalQ) that shift between enterprise-grade objections and conversational self-interrogation. Pacing oscillates between [extended five-item lists](narr:StyleObs_6) that push the limits of triadic rhythm and [short, punchy declarative sentences](narr:StyleObs_ShortPunchy) that serve as emphatic anchors. The text also employs [anaphoric repetition](narr:StyleObs_Anaphora) to establish scale, while [sailing-metaphor self-corrections](narr:StyleObs_4) introduce a layer of spoken, self-aware register that contrasts with the otherwise polished, parallel syntax. Together, these devices create a tension between the systematic, version-controlled tone of the product and a more human, conversational cadence.""" ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Observation_GitNativeTriad> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_10> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_4> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_6> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_Anaphora> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_RhetoricalQ> ;
    narr:covers <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_ShortPunchy> ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "git native, i.e. versionable, branchable, reviewable" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#Observation_GitNativeTriad> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "explicit, reviewable, and testable" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_10> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "positioning, offering, product, teams, and process" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_6> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "every single home, but every single venture, every single backend, every surface" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_Anaphora> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "We have a lot of knowledge locked in people's heads." ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_ShortPunchy> ] ;
    narr:keyPhrase [ narr:text "They serve as telltales. That's the right word. They serve as telltales" ; narr:phraseSource <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_4> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The [sailing-metaphor self-correction](narr:StyleObs_4) introduces a spontaneous, spoken-word register that breaks the document's rigid parallel structure." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_4> ] ;
    narr:variation [ narr:text "The [five-item list](narr:StyleObs_6) pushes against the document's dominant 'rule of three' rhythm, favoring exhaustive completeness over triadic brevity." ; narr:over <https://aswritten.ai/ns/narrative#StyleObs_6> ] ;
    narr:writer "google/gemini-3.1-flash-lite" .
